\f1\b Step 3 .- 
\f0\b0 Type $git rebase GitHubBasicLab1/your_name/exercise1\
If there are any file conflicts, resolve them and continue with the rebase.\
Type $git log  - -graph. Add a screenshot as evidence.\

\f1\b Step 4
\f0\b0 .- push your new branch GitHubBasicLab1/your_name/exercise3 to origin. Type $git push origin GitHubBasicLab1/your_name/exercise1\

