\f1\b Step 6
\f0\b0 .- Approve and merge your PR.\

\f1\b Step 7
\f0\b0 .- switch to your previous branch GitHubBasicLab1/your_name/exercise1, and delete your GitHubBasicLab1/your_name/exercise3 branch\

\f1\b Step 8
